We don't have very long together
and Harry and I were trying

00:03:27.270 --> 00:03:30.790
to figure out how to do this to
maximize it and we both agreed

00:03:30.790 --> 00:03:33.570
that what we would like to do
is to talk with you all as much

00:03:33.570 --> 00:03:39.760
as possible and Harry also
volunteered that he could have,

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:43.730
do I get this right, a
volunteer come up and do a.

