[ Inaudible Question ]

00:08:45.830 --> 00:08:48.630
My favorite book that
I ever wrote myself?

00:08:48.630 --> 00:08:51.780
Are you here with
a parental unit?

00:08:51.780 --> 00:08:53.440
Where is that parental unit?

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:56.220
Oh, somewhere over there, okay.

00:08:56.220 --> 00:08:59.000
And do you have brothers
and sisters?

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:02.680
So, where is the
mother of this child?

00:09:02.680 --> 00:09:05.550
Because I've got a
question for you which is,

00:09:05.550 --> 00:09:09.570
which of the children
do you love the best?

00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:13.340
And I know, I know what
your mom would say.

