"I love them equally,
but differently"

00:09:16.470 --> 00:09:18.330
and that's the same way I feel

00:09:18.330 --> 00:09:20.080
about any books that
I've written.

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:23.340
I see them as like deeply
flawed but loveable anyway

00:09:23.340 --> 00:09:25.770
which is I'm not saying you're
deeply flawed, you seem lovely,

00:09:25.770 --> 00:09:27.190
but do you know what I mean?

00:09:27.190 --> 00:09:31.700
There are just, I feel intense
love for them that's equal

00:09:31.700 --> 00:09:34.180
but I see them as individuals.

00:09:35.390 --> 00:09:37.370
Yes.

